name: Air Canada E-190 landing at Vancouver International Airport
description:
Hello everyone, this is an onboard video of an Air Canada Embraer 190 landing at Vancouver International Airport (CYVR/YVR), arriving from LAX. I hope you enjoy the video!

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
